data.description: Luxurious 3-Bed Condo, Stunning Pond Views! Discover modern luxury in this meticulously maintained 3-bed, 2.5-bath condo. With 1,980 sq ft of living space, it offers a serene lifestyle in the highly desirable Washington Township location. Ready to move in and enjoy!  Check out the impressive Upgrades. Highlights include a renovated kitchen (2021) with granite countertops, marble backsplash, and Samsung smart refrigerator and oven/stove! New LVP (Luxury Vinyl Plank) flooring on all of the second level (kitchen, dining, living, 1/2 bath) (2023) and new carpet on the stairs to third level and throughout the hallway and all three bedrooms (2021). A new water softener (2019), and a new exterior AC unit (2021) add to the appeal. (Over $54,000 in updates) Enjoy elegant living in this open-concept main level, flooded with natural light!  Cozy evenings in front of your fireplace and morning coffee or evening toddy on your back deck overlooking the picturesque pond (new, composite 2023). Spacious Bedrooms on the 3rd level include the primary bedroom, which boasts a walk-in closet and a private bathroom with a double vanity and large walk-in shower. Two additional bedrooms, located away from the primary bedroom, offer walk-in closets and share a full hall bath. The lower level features a tandem 2-car garage with storage and access out back to the pond. Potential for extra living space if finished. Community/HOA perks include in-ground pool, pool house and walking paths!  HOA covers snow removal, lawn maintenance, water, and exterior homeowners insurance. Prime Location, location, location! Easy access to I-675 and I-75, this amazing condo is located in Washington TWP (no city taxes) and within the acclaimed Centerville School District. Close to Austin Landing, shopping, and dining among other amenities,  his condo offers an exquisite blend of luxury and convenience. Contact your Realtor today for a private tour. Don't miss this opportunity!
